+OPPO A1K / CPH1923 (project 18540) target files.
+
+The target uses the MT6765 LK platform with the board-specific 144 MiB scratch
+layout, OPPO boot arguments, key map, display geometry, charger configuration,
+and public AVB/OEM verification keys. See ../../docs/OPPO_A1K_PORT.md for the
+porting notes and safety constraints.
